<div class='description'>
Benjamin is a fun, active, loving African American child. He has dark brown eyes and light brown skin color. He is always eager to please others, communicates well and always has a smile on his face. Benjamin is a friendly and active young boy. He enjoys sports, watching cartoons, watching movies, using computers and playing video games. Benjamin is excited about joining a forever family. His only request to be able to maintain contact with his grandmother. Benjamin requires a forever family who is patient and consistent in setting rules, boundaries, and consequences.
